---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Button from '@/components/ui/Button.astro';
import Card from '@/components/ui/Card.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="參與 Bitcoin Core 開發"
  description="了解如何為 Bitcoin Core 專案做出貢獻。"
>
  <!-- Hero section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-[var(--bg-secondary)] to-[var(--bg-primary)]">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <nav class="mb-8" aria-label="麵包屑">
        <ol class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-tertiary)]">
          <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-[var(--text-primary)]">首頁</a></li>
          <li>/</li>
          <li><a href="/tech/" class="hover:text-[var(--text-primary)]">技術</a></li>
          <li>/</li>
          <li><a href="/tech/bitcoin-core/" class="hover:text-[var(--text-primary)]">Bitcoin Core</a></li>
          <li>/</li>
          <li class="text-[var(--text-primary)]">參與開發</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-6">
          參與 Bitcoin Core 開發
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-[var(--text-secondary)]">
          Bitcoin Core 是一個開源專案，歡迎任何人參與貢獻。
          無論是程式碼、文檔、測試還是代碼審查，都是寶貴的貢獻。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ways to contribute -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-12 text-center">
        貢獻方式
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <Card padding="lg">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-2">程式碼貢獻</h3>
          <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
            修復 bug、實現新功能或改進現有代碼。所有的 PR 都需要經過嚴格的審查流程。
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)]">
            <li>• 熟悉 C++ 和比特幣協議</li>
            <li>• 閱讀貢獻指南和代碼風格</li>
            <li>• 從小的改進開始</li>
          </ul>
        </Card>

        <Card padding="lg">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-green-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-2">代碼審查</h3>
          <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
            審查其他人的 PR 是非常重要的貢獻。Bitcoin Core 的變更需要多人審查才能合併。
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)]">
            <li>• 理解變更的目的和影響</li>
            <li>• 測試變更是否正常運作</li>
            <li>• 提供建設性的反饋</li>
          </ul>
        </Card>

        <Card padding="lg">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-purple-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-purple-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-2">文檔撰寫</h3>
          <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
            改進文檔、撰寫教程或翻譯現有文檔，幫助更多人理解 Bitcoin Core。
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)]">
            <li>• 改進 README 和 Wiki</li>
            <li>• 撰寫開發者教程</li>
            <li>• 翻譯文檔到其他語言</li>
          </ul>
        </Card>

        <Card padding="lg">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-yellow-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-yellow-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-2">回報問題</h3>
          <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
            發現 bug 或有改進建議？在 GitHub 上開啟 Issue 進行討論。
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)]">
            <li>• 詳細描述問題</li>
            <li>• 提供重現步驟</li>
            <li>• 包含相關日誌和環境資訊</li>
          </ul>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Resources -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-[var(--bg-secondary)]">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-12 text-center">
        開始之前
      </h2>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 rounded-lg bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-default)] hover:border-bitcoin-500 transition-colors"
        >
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)]">CONTRIBUTING.md</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)]">官方貢獻指南</p>
          </div>
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-[var(--text-tertiary)]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://bitcoincore.reviews/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 rounded-lg bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-default)] hover:border-bitcoin-500 transition-colors"
        >
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)]">Bitcoin Core PR Review Club</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)]">每週 PR 審查學習小組</p>
          </div>
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-[var(--text-tertiary)]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://chaincode.gitbook.io/seminars/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 rounded-lg bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-default)] hover:border-bitcoin-500 transition-colors"
        >
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)]">Chaincode Seminars</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)]">比特幣和閃電網路開發者培訓</p>
          </div>
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-[var(--text-tertiary)]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-wide text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-4">
        準備好開始了嗎？
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        訪問 Bitcoin Core 的 GitHub 倉庫，開始你的貢獻之旅。
      </p>
      <Button href="https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin" variant="primary" size="lg" external>
        前往 GitHub
      </Button>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
